text: Chernolesovsky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Krasnoyarsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,118 as of 2010. There are 20 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Ufa, 17 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Chernolesovsky
